title: MisterMusic Show 298 - New indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 298 -2 hours 192 kbps MP3



I have new songs from Cymbals, Panama, Saintseneca and another new track off the latest Elbow album.
Plus we travel back 21 years for a number 1 modern rock hit from April 1993.
A song that was one of the band's highest charting songs.

All that plus the usual eclectic mix of new and classic tunes.
Broadcasting weekly, and heard globally on the web on Rock XS Radio-it's the MisterMusic Show.
